The Proposal:
Jijamata Educational Institute, Phule Nagar, Nanded Operated Jijamata Primary School, Phulenagar, Nanded
This Marathi medium of primary (e.g. 1st to 4th aided and 5th to 7th partially aided) School, Shri.
In a letter regarding transfer of management to Sharda Bhawan Education Society, Nanded.
The proposal received was under the consideration of the government.
The government's decision:
The management of the school was transferred to Shri Sharda Bhawan Education Society, Nanded.
The Government has decided to grant approval on the following terms and conditions: -
(1) The condition of minimum marks of the school to which the management is transferred is relaxed for any reason.
Won't go.
(2) Any conditions of Government permission / approval in respect of the school to which the management has been transferred, and
Care should be taken not to change the conditions.
(3) From time to time, in respect of schools, teachers / non-teaching staff, salary / non-salary grants, students, etc. by the Government.
The new body will be bound to comply with the prescribed Acts, Rules, Orders, etc.
(4) This Management Transfer, Government Decision, Department of School Education and Sports, No: Mashah 2011 / (210/11)
MASHI-3 shall come into force in accordance with the rules and procedures prescribed on 17th February, 2012.
(5) The transfer of this management to the Government or to the field officers of the Department of Education.
If a complaint is received or it is found that there is a breach of the terms and conditions regarding the transfer of management
or the new allowances of the teaching / non-teaching staff working in the institution before the transfer of management.
In the event of a breach by the organization, the government will have the power to cancel the management transfer.
Government Decision Number: PRASHAH-3024 / Q. 330/24 SM-1
The Deputy Director of Zonal Education, Latur Division, Latur has examined all the aspects and the above terms / conditions.
Further action on transfer of management of the school within 15 days, including additional necessary conditions.
Do it and inform the government about it.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
